# BuzzWorld Daily Intel

Automated daily intelligence reports generated from **public sources only**, powered by **GitHub Actions**.

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-brightgreen)
![Automation](https://img.shields.io/badge/automation-GitHub%20Actions-blue)
![Schedule](https://img.shields.io/badge/schedule-daily%2006%3A00%20UTC-orange)

---

## What This Is

A lightweight, transparent automation that:

- Runs daily at **06:00 UTC**
- Pulls selected public documentation
- Generates a report
- Commits changes automatically
- Preserves a full audit trail via Git history

No credentials.  
No private data.  
No hidden behavior.

---

## How It Works

1. GitHub Actions runs on a daily cron
2. Public documentation is fetched
3. A report is written to `reports/daily.md`
4. Changes are committed by a bot identity
5. History remains fully inspectable

---

